<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$mu-se" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/mu-se" class="zg-link" title="虹心">虹心</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$kou-jie" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/kou-jie" class="zg-link" title="寇捷">寇捷</a></span>
